{"tid":1637343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光頭警長微博鬧法官 我地要幫佢聲音傳送比法官知","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:47:24.000Z","uid":282650,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b2cd53b7bb2ca959bb4db8b0baac60774f415e46","tid":1637343,"uid":282650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"法官唔會個個睇微博，佢講完法官收唔到就浪費左佢一番心血。<br />\n小弟draft左template信幫一幫佢推下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnFk3hM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnFk3hM.png&h=5346b5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nenquiry@judiciary.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\nDear Sir/Madam in Magistrates&rsquo; Courts<br />\n<br />\nI write to inform a suspected case of contempt of court regarding a police officer published a speech in social media slandering the magistrates and suspected violating S.99 of Cap. 227.<br />\nThe police officer, Stationary Sergeant LAU Cha-kei, published a post on Weibo, (Link: <a href=\"https://www.weibo.cn/detail/4424799634260958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.cn%2Fdetail%2F4424799634260958&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e74705d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.cn/detail/4424799634260958</a>), insulting magistrates who had made decisions not to sign on an urgent search warrant requested by the police.  He slandered that the magistrates concerned were encouraging rioters to commit crimes which is obviously a serious accusation towards them.  His speech got thousands people commenting and &ldquo;like&rdquo; with more than a thousand share via the page, resulting a huge damage and threatening to independence of judiciary in Hong Kong. <br />\nI hereby urging the Judiciary to report the case to police for their enforcement and other necessary action to take.  </span></span><br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\nMr/Ms XXX<br />\nCitizen of Hong Kong SAR<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人少佢地當睇唔到就算，多人send就要回應架啦，推埋比記者朋友睇"},{"pid":"788751cbdcd2bf2f6bc31797e87b8590f6816623","tid":1637343,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"支持行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"7d7ba846eaf867c597cc7cc0be257edc7c9d5b33","tid":1637343,"uid":260022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:10:48.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"cd3a189cb8f4aea4624b40abb48149f62db79bf6","tid":1637343,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb83b8e8c8423d92c5df7d7fdebb8f96f475baaf","tid":1637343,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72e9182c901bc93ca5dbc13b7917d1f3eac0c2b","tid":1637343,"uid":246520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n但可執執grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f80a86291ae2aad1499ccc4d59f922c815be64","tid":1637343,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"光頭警長想煽動愛國撚私了法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d61fa8e74632ad6ccb6ea1a7cf5b60b6d2f130","tid":1637343,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:14:21.000Z